$PAR
True or false:
If \(\lbrace x_n \rbrace_{n=1}^\infty\) is a bounded sequence and
\(a_n := \sup \lbrace x_k : k \geq n \rbrace , \)
then \(\lbrace a_n \rbrace_{n=1}^\infty\) is a subsequence of \(\lbrace x_n \rbrace_{n=1}^\infty .\)
$BR
END_TEXT
