BEGIN_TEXT
\{ $q1->buttons \}

$PAR
True or false:
If \(\liminf \, x_n $LTS \limsup \, x_n ,\) then
\(\lbrace x_n \rbrace_{n=1}^\infty\) diverges.
$BR
END_TEXT
Context()->normalStrings;

